  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: AAAAARRRGGHHH
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: aaaaaa!! ce s-a intamplat??
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: nu un om... NU IAR
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "nu \u0219tiu cum s\u0103 r\u0103spund"
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: nu mai suport! e horror
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "nu o s\u0103 \xEEmi cer iertare c\u0103 sunt om, s\u0103 \u0219tii!"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "plant\u0103.. uria\u0219\u0103 \u0219i ciudat\u0103 ce e\u0219ti!"
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: "CIUDAT\u0102"
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: "TU e\u0219ti o CIUDAT\u0102"
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: "\xEEmi sun\u0103 a rasism"
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: "se pronun\u021B\u0103 \"realism\""
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: ughhh
  choices:
  - choiceText: "ce e cu libr\u0103ria asta?"
